Since the luminosity can be different for each colliding bunch pair, both because the beam sizes can vary bunch-to-bunch but also because the bunch population product n1n2 can vary at the level of 10–20 %, the determination of Σx/y and the measurement of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
