The value of μvis is determined from the raw event rate using the analytic function described in Sect. 4.1 for the inclusive EventOR algorithms. The coincidence EventAND algorithms are more involved, and a numerical inversion is performed to determine μvis from the raw EventAND rate. Since the EventAND μ determination depends on \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
